{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There, we were greeted by some charming, lovely French farmers, who pushed their arms on us and welcomed us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when we got there, all they had to offer us was some very sour and cheap vino.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was about-- I was 13 or-- no, I was 14.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What I wanted was a glass of milk or a cup of tea or coffee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it didn't put me off for life, but it put me off of wine for a very long time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Our destinations, according to the passeur, was Grenoble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We actually wanted to go to Nice, which was nicknamed the refugees' town because there were consulates there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But we were told to go to Grenoble because there, we would be given ration cards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I think French-- [INAUDIBLE] French [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there's no one I can ask anymore because they're dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I know that we had ration cards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "In Grenoble, we went to a little hotel called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't know-- I presume-- you know, we-- what we paid to get across did not include the cost of this little hotel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was a bitterly cold winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my brother and I knew at that time that there was a visa waiting for-- an entry visa waiting for us in Lisbon, Portugal because the British allowed German refugees and parents of refugees, not brothers or sisters.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So really, somehow or other, we had to get across to Portugal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We knew that people crossed the Pyrenees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we made inquiries.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They would've taken my brother but not me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They thought I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
